    <ShortLegislativeSummaryEn>&lt;div&gt;A legislative summary is currently being prepared for this bill by the Parliamentary Information, Education and Research Services of the Library of Parliament. Meanwhile, the following executive summary is available.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;On 26 March 2026, the Minister of Crown-Indigenous Relations introduced Bill C-27, An Act to give effect to the Final Self-Government Agreement for the Tlegohli Got’ine and to make consequential amendments to other Acts (Final Self-Government Agreement for the Tlegohli Got’ine Act) in the House of Commons and it was given first reading.   &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Bill C-27 gives effect to the Final Self-Government Agreement for the Tlego´hli? Got’ine and makes consequential amendments to other Acts.&lt;/div&gt;</ShortLegislativeSummaryEn>
    <ShortLegislativeSummaryFr>&lt;div&gt;Les Service d’information, d’éducation et de recherche parlementaires de la Bibliothèque du Parlement rédige actuellement le résumé législatif de ce projet de loi.  Entre-temps, le Service met à votre disposition le sommaire suivant.  &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Le 26 mars 2026, le ministre des Relations Couronne-Autochtones a déposé le projet de loi C-27, Loi portant mise en vigueur de l’accord définitif sur l’autonomie gouvernementale des Tlegohli Got’ine et modifiant certaines lois en conséquence (Loi sur l’accord définitif sur l’autonomie gouvernementale des Tlegohli Got’ine) à la Chambre des communes en première lecture. &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Le projet de loi C-27 met en vigueur l’accord définitif sur l’autonomie gouvernementale des Tlego´hli? Got’ine et modifie certaines lois en conséquence.&lt;/div&gt;</ShortLegislativeSummaryFr>
    <ShortLegislativeSummary>&lt;div&gt;A legislative summary is currently being prepared for this bill by the Parliamentary Information, Education and Research Services of the Library of Parliament. Meanwhile, the following executive summary is available.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;On 26 March 2026, the Minister of Crown-Indigenous Relations introduced Bill C-27, An Act to give effect to the Final Self-Government Agreement for the Tlegohli Got’ine and to make consequential amendments to other Acts (Final Self-Government Agreement for the Tlegohli Got’ine Act) in the House of Commons and it was given first reading.   &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Bill C-27 gives effect to the Final Self-Government Agreement for the Tlego´hli? Got’ine and makes consequential amendments to other Acts.&lt;/div&gt;</ShortLegislativeSummary>
